data.title: Welcome to the Florida Education Fund Online
data.meta_description:
Established in 1984, the FEF's mission is to strengthen the larger community by creating and 
implementing programs and services that lead to institutional enhancement and greater educational advancement for historically 
underrepresented groups.
data.text:
Dissertation Fellowships

The program provides up to one year of funding for stipends, professional development activity and counseling to selected Florida Ph.D. students working to complete dissertations in STEM disciplines.
